<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يقول في <span class="c3">{ساحرَانِ تَظَاهَرَا}</span> يعنون الإنجيل والقرآن <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
